Zero point energy                ...      0.28487765 Eh     178.76 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.01581373 Eh       9.92 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
